<!-- Hero -->



<div class="container">

    <div class="row mt-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h1 id="slogan" class="grays">Sometimes all it takes is an angry cat<br></h1>
        <p>For yourself or your hideous neighbour,<br>for a day or for the whole month.<br>Rent a variety of nasty felines on our platform.</p>
        <h3>Get ready for the next scratch!</h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row text-center mt-5">
      <h4>Top 3 angriest cats</h5>
      <div class="col-lg-12 d-flex justify-content-around gx-3 mt-3">
          <div class="col-sm-3">
            <div class="card my-8">
                <img src="https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/00/68/33/03/360_F_68330331_dKqChy33w0TcNHJEkqT5iw97QOX8la7F.jpg">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="card-title text-center">Voldemort</h6>
                  <%= link_to "Book me", cat_path(Cat.first), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-3">
            <div class="card my-8">
                <img src="https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/00/68/33/03/360_F_68330331_dKqChy33w0TcNHJEkqT5iw97QOX8la7F.jpg">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="card-title text-center">Saruman</h6>
                  <%= link_to "Book me", cat_path(Cat.second), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-3">
            <div class="card my-8">
                <img src="https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/00/68/33/03/360_F_68330331_dKqChy33w0TcNHJEkqT5iw97QOX8la7F.jpg">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="card-title text-center">Mephisto</h6>
                  <%= link_to "Book me", cat_path(Cat.third), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6 text-center text-white mt-5">
      <div class="rounded-3 bg-primary p-3">
        <h4>How it works</h4>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li class="list-group-item">1. Look for an angry cat in your neighborhood</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">2. Send a request to the owner</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">3. Go pick the angry creature up and... deal with it!</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6 text-center text-white mt-5">
      <div class="rounded-3 bg-primary p-3">
        <h4>What our customers say</h4>
        <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
        <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
        <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
        <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
        <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
        <p>Extraordinary! The cat sent my boss to hospital <strong>in no time</strong> so he couldn't fire me! Watch out, <strong>these cats are the scariest</strong> out there.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
